name: Layout
description: Represents the metadata associated with a page layout.

custombuttons.name: customButtons
custombuttons.description: The custom buttons for this layout.

customconsolecomponents.name: customConsoleComponents
customconsolecomponents.description: Represents custom console components (Visualforce pages, lookup fields, or related lists) on a page layout.

emaildefault.name: emailDefault
emaildefault.description: Default value for the email checkbox. Only relevant if the showEmailCheckbox property is set.

excludebuttons.name: excludeButtons
excludebuttons.description: List of standard buttons to exclude from this layout.

feedlayout.name: feedLayout
feedlayout.description: Represents the values that define the feed view of a feed-based page layout.

headers.name: headers
headers.description: Represents the layout headers used for tagging.

layoutsections.name: layoutSections
layoutsections.description: The main sections of the layout containing fields, s-controls, and custom links. The order here determines the layout order.

minilayout.name: miniLayout
minilayout.description: Represents a minilayout, which is used in the mini view of a record in the Console tab, hover details, and event overlays.

multilinelayoutfields.name: multilineLayoutFields
multilinelayoutfields.description: Fields for special multiline layout fields which appear in OpportunityProduct layouts.

platformactionlist.name: platformActionList
platformactionlist.description: The list of actions, and their order, that display in the Salesforce mobile action bar for the layout.

quickactionlist.name: quickActionList
quickactionlist.description: The list of quick actions that display in the full Salesforce site for the page layout.

relatedcontent.name: relatedContent
relatedcontent.description: The Related Content section of the page layout.

relatedlists.name: relatedLists
relatedlists.description: The related lists for the layout, listed in the order they appear in the user interface.

relatedobjects.name: relatedObjects
relatedobjects.description: The list of related objects that appears in the mini view of the console.

runassignmentrulesdefault.name: runAssignmentRulesDefault
runassignmentrulesdefault.description: Default value for the “run assignment rules” checkbox. Only relevant if the showRunAssignmentRulesCheckbox property is set.

showemailcheckbox.name: showEmailCheckbox
showemailcheckbox.description: Controls whether to show the email checkbox. Only allowed on Case, CaseClose, and Task layouts. The default state of checkbox is controlled by the emailDefault property.

showhighlightspanel.name: showHighlightsPanel
showhighlightspanel.description: If set, the highlights panel displays on pages in the Salesforce console.

showinteractionlogpanel.name: showInteractionLogPanel
showinteractionlogpanel.description: If set, the interaction log displays on pages in the Salesforce console.

showknowledgecomponent.name: showKnowledgeComponent
showknowledgecomponent.description: Only allowed on Case layouts. If set, the Knowledge sidebar displays on cases in the Salesforce console.

showrunassignmentrulescheckbox.name: showRunAssignmentRulesCheckbox
showrunassignmentrulescheckbox.description: Controls whether to show the Run Assignment Rules checkbox. Only allowed on Lead and Case layouts. The default state of checkbox is controlled by the runAssignmentRulesDefault property.

showsolutionsection.name: showSolutionSection
showsolutionsection.description: Only allowed on CaseClose layout. If set, the built-in solution information section shows up on the page.

showsubmitandattachbutton.name: showSubmitAndAttachButton
showsubmitandattachbutton.description: For Cast layouts only. If set, the Submit & Add Attachment button displays on case edit pages to portal users in the Customer Portal.

summarylayout.name: summaryLayout
summarylayout.description: The summary layout for this layout.

clone().name: clone
clone().description: Makes a duplicate copy of the Metadata.Layout.
